    "body": "That would be a pretty big change. I mean, this has been like this (despite our pleas) since day 1 ...\r\n\r\nHaving said that, I've been adding SetCurrentDirectory into my prompt since my first prompt function, so I can't really think of any reason *not* to fix this, except the classic: It's bound to break **something** ðŸ˜‹ðŸ˜‹\r\n",
